data.title: Artist: Bob Dylan
data.meta_description: Bob Dylan covered The Night We Called It a Day, That Old Feeling, Silver Bells, Slow Train and other songs. Bob Dylan originally did Silver Bells, The Night We Called It a Day, Slow Train, Hero Blues and other songs. Bob Dylan wrote Knockin' on Heaven's Door, Rise and All Along the Watchtower.
